        Family Law Property Orders and Selling Brisbane Property: What Separating Couples Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Selling jointly owned Brisbane property after separation requires specific legal steps many couples are not aware of. Here is what the process looks like and what to do before you contact a real estate agent.
      </p>
